In-game pitch count must be derived from ordered Statcast pitches per `(game_pk, pitcher_id)` using game-local order, not the raw at-bat pitch number.[3]

### Layer C: Times Through Order Splits

Grain: pitcher-TTO-season

#### Table: `sp_tto_splits`

| Field | Description |
|---|---|
| `pitcher_id` | Pitcher |
| `tto` | 1, 2, 3 where 3 means third-or-later |
